data.description: Unique opportunity. Lake county purchased the lots on each side of this house. The houses on the east & west of the house have been torn down. These spaces can never be built on. It's like having 3 lots for the price of 1. Tranquil, bright & wonderful home on huge wooded lot. Sunshine pours thru 3 skylights if this modern mid-century ranch home w/a spacious flowing layout & gorgeous wood floors. Two master suites, over 2500 square feet. Stone fireplace graces living room. Huge Family room addition w/2nd master suite & balcony overlooking fenced yard.  Finished basement w/abundant storage. Newer roof. Water heater, 2 air conditioners, 2 heaters, washing machine, dishwasher & refrigerator all 3 years ago. Two & a half car garage. Flood insurance  required. Backs to forest preserve. Quiet street. Kipling school district. A treasure. Agent related to seller.
